## Finding: Hypothetical Real-World Failure Walk-Through — "The SaaS Startup That Uses This Framework"

### Gap Type: FAILURE_MODE_UNCOVERED
### Severity: CRITICAL
### Evidence:
Simulating a real-world SaaS startup using this framework end-to-end reveals the following friction points in order of occurrence:

