**Scope**: Complete SRE practice foundation. Covers: SLO definition templates (availability, latency, error rate targets with measurement methodology), error budget calculation and burn rate alerting, toil identification and elimination framework (what counts as toil, quarterly toil audit process), blameless postmortem template (5-why analysis, contributing factors, action items with owners and deadlines), on-call rotation design (primary/secondary, escalation policy, runbook quality standards), reliability review cadence (weekly reliability review, monthly SLO review, quarterly capacity review).
